{"tid":1847071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"現行世界衞生組織的《國際衞生條例》所列疾病不包括武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-28T01:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:46:49.000Z","uid":12599,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb24f930a4c4bdd56e7813403a78a85c00e5aec","tid":1847071,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"HA高層講緊指引做事, 我就同你地玩指引<br />\n<br />\n跟返HA既指引:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/cs/WHO_IHR_B5.pdf?fbclid=IwAR3sKXd16y9M7mfuSTMKTEghwTt1TDdODlF3AQDJatZ1jjMTVEQYhTDkiGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fhaho%2Fho%2Fcs%2FWHO_IHR_B5.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3sKXd16y9M7mfuSTMKTEghwTt1TDdODlF3AQDJatZ1jjMTVEQYhTDkiGw&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=1795f5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/cs/WHO_IHR_B5.pdf?fbclid=IwAR3sKXd16y9M7mfuSTMKTEghwTt1TDdODlF3AQDJatZ1jjMTVEQYhTDkiGw</a><br />\n中文版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/cs/WHO_IHR_EN.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fhaho%2Fho%2Fcs%2FWHO_IHR_EN.pdf&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=835ea74f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/cs/WHO_IHR_EN.pdf</a><br />\n英文版<br />\n<br />\n如有出入均以英文為準<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現行世界衞生組織的《國際衞生條例》所列疾病</span></span></strong><br />\n(a) 可能構成國際關注的突發公共衛生事件的疾病，在世界衞生組織的機制下，任何單一病<br />\n例都需即時向世界衞生組織通報<br />\n- 新亞型病毒引起的人流感 (Human influenza caused by a new subtype)<br />\n- 由野毒株引起的脊髓灰質炎 (Poliomyelitis due to wild-type poliovirus)<br />\n- 嚴重急性呼吸道綜合症（SARS）<br />\n- 天花 (Smallpox)<br />\n(b) 可能造成嚴重衛生影響並能在國際上迅速傳播的疾病<br />\n- 霍亂（及其他腸道傳染的流行病）(Cholera (and other epidemic diarrhoeal disease))<br />\n- 肺鼠疫 (Pneumonic plague)<br />\n- 病毒性出血熱（埃博拉熱、拉薩熱、馬爾堡熱、西尼羅熱）(Viral haemorrhagic fevers (Ebola, Lassa, Marburg, West Nile fever))<br />\n- 黃熱病 (Yellow fever)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">WHO自2005年後就無update過呢個表</span>, 即係全世界收MERS同WARS都唔使跟垃圾WHO指引做事, 因為呢兩隻病唔係指引入面<br />\n<br />\n如果HA夠膽唔收WARS病人錢, 我告撚到你班官Hihi呀"},{"pid":"f2e009d67f581bd84addeec21e1ad72786afd1f7","tid":1847071,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"42074bf9e8b01b361fda1c8c230e25fd6d6f882a","tid":1847071,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府"},{"pid":"962af49c1385a544a154991b763f36ccf3dd9da5","tid":1847071,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"d0713ad10b801e26de81fe040703004e28068d38","tid":1847071,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"支持入稟"},{"pid":"61b6b6daabca0f6ecfb3df340d4eaf870e1480e9","tid":1847071,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c35fc1eb622eeec7e9cbbd62fd94a48fefbd5a2","tid":1847071,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"297353af585ad05415f7efaa25deba0432eefefa","tid":1847071,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48007ec8b9c87b174554d1973a25f4860006152","tid":1847071,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"297353af585ad05415f7efaa25deba0432eefefa","tid":1847071,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" clas